Smiley
-----------
Setup:
Create your own "database/settings.php" file (from "database/default.settings.php") with database settings
Create your own "client/js/config.js" file (from "client/js/default.config.js") with serverlocation
Create your own "stats/js/config.js" file (from "stats/js/default.config.js") with serverlocation

The web client is located in client/
The statistics page is located in stats/

The SQL to setup the DB is here: "database/init_database.sql"
